<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡A mi pancita le encantaría!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Ah<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /> era eso,<delay8 /> sí.<20_2 arg="2" /><delay8 /> Ya caigo.<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Lechuga con tacos al pastor<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="6" />Mira, <tag a="110" b="3" />, no le digas esas cosas a <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />, ¡que se cree todo!<pageBreak />Es capaz de hacerse una ensalada
