	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />¡<tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="3" />!<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 /> No le digas esas cosas,<delay8 /> que se las puede creer,<delay8 /> <anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡y vamos a tener un disgusto!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Tiburones, claro!<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 /> ¿Cómo se me pudo
olvidar?<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /> Qué despiste tengo.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">¿En serio, <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />?<20_2 arg="1" /><delay8 /> <anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¿Tiburones?<delay8 /> ¿No te suena peligroso?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Bueno, muy comunes no son<20_2 arg="2" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Nunca los he probado, la verdad,<delay8 />
